title: BEWARE:Mold
review: I had this yogurt delivered from my local Whole Foods on Sunday. It's now Wednesday and I went to eat the yogurt and found mold. It's hard to see, but the lid lists an expiration date of 08/30/21. Mold before the product expires? Not cheap yogurt to be wasted.
